uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.session

Interface RequiredPage<U extends AppUser>

  • Type Parameters:
    U - type of AppUser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppUserFactory.UpdatePersonRequiredPage, DatabasePasswordComposite.PasswordResetRequiredPage

    public interface RequiredPage<U extends AppUser>
    Object representing a page that a user is redirected to if certain conditions are met. e.g. a password reset page. You must ensure that any JSP referenced in this way does not include the redirect checks itself. Composites in the AppUserFactory can add these if they implement RequiredPageProvider

    spb
